{{Conjecture|legends}}
This '''laundry service''' in [[Gadrin]] was run by an elderly pair of [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustans]]. A large portion of its business was the cleaning of uniforms for local companies, such as [[House Hirskaala]] and [[Renna's Transport Service]].<ref name="ACP">{{LivingForce|Eye of the Sun: A Cularin Presence}}</ref>

In [[31 BBY/Legends|31 BBY]], on two days in a row, the laundry service was robbed of the uniforms they had cleaned. These uniforms were then used by the [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] who stole them to help in hijacking goods from the businesses the uniforms belonged to.<ref name="ACP" />

